        <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed italic">Dolphin Centrifuge designs disc stack centrifuge systems with all eight external performance factors built into the system layout — proper feed tank sizing, pump selection, discharge piping, and ambient temperature management. These installation decisions determine whether a centrifuge achieves its rated capacity. Based in Warren, Michigan, Dolphin Centrifuge has over 40 years of experience in centrifuge system engineering and installation.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Intro with hero image -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm p-6 md:p-8 mb-8">
