        <p class="text-text leading-relaxed mb-4">Disc stack centrifuge performance depends on several factors that are internal and external. Internal factors are those which are related to the centrifuge and the process fluid.</p>
        <p class="text-text leading-relaxed mb-4">We will discuss the external factors here. You can also read our blog about <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-efficiency/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">internal factors that affect centrifuge efficiency</a>.</p>
        <div class="bg-navy/5 border border-navy/20 rounded-lg p-4">
          <p class="text-navy font-semibold"><a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-faq/" class="hover:text-gold transition-colors">Read our 101 Frequently Asked Questions about Disc Stack Centrifuges!</a></p>
        </div>
